data.description: Welcome to your new home!  Wonderful rancher on cul-de-sac in Lake Park. 3 Bedrooms, 1.5 Baths. Hardwood floors and replacement windows.  You will enjoy cooking with gas in the kitchen or grilling out on the patio. Relax in the spacious backyard with summer activities and beautiful water views to round out the experience. 1 car attached garage.  Perfectly centrally within minutes of shopping, dining and the interstate.  A must see!
